OL,3,CScottish Government 'floundering' on
OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,FA marine sustainability charity has
OL,7,Faccused the Scottish Government of
OL,8,F"floundering" over its plans for
OL,9,Fmanaging Scotland's fisheries post-
OL,10,FBrexit.
OL,12,FOpen Seas, which campaigns for
OL,13,Fsustainable fishing, said the
OL,14,Fgovernment's failure to meet a 2024
OL,15,Ftarget for the delivery of fisheries
OL,16,Fmanagement plans (FMPs) for 22
OL,17,FScottish fisheries was undermining
OL,18,Fefforts to ensure long-term
OL,19,Fsustainability and biodiversity in
OL,20,FScotland's seas.
