OL,3,CScottish Government 'floundering' on
OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,FUnder the 2022 Joint Fisheries
OL,7,FStatement agreed by all four UK
OL,8,Fnational governments, the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment committed to producing 22
OL,10,FFMPs by 2024 for the sustainable
OL,11,Fmanagement of key stocks in Scottish
OL,12,Fwaters.
OL,14,FThese include cod, herring, haddock
OL,15,Fand nephrops (better known as scampi
OL,16,For langoustine).
