OL,3,CScottish Government 'floundering' on
OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,FHowever on Thursday Secretary for
OL,7,FRural Affairs Mairi Gougeon confirmed
OL,8,Fthe deadlines for completion of the
OL,9,Fplans needed to be "amended", and that
OL,10,Fa consultation on delaying them to the
OL,11,Fend of 2026 was under way.
OL,13,F"A significant amount of work has
OL,14,Falready been completed, however, this
OL,15,Fwork is complex and further
OL,16,Fstakeholder engagement and
OL,17,Fconsultation is needed," she said.
