OL,3,CScottish Government 'floundering' on
OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,F"The statutory deadlines therefore
OL,7,Fneed to be amended to ensure the right
OL,8,Ftime and space to develop and deliver
OL,9,Frobust and effective plans."
OL,11,FOpen Seas said this explanation
OL,12,Fappeared to be a "smokescreen" for
OL,13,Fdelays caused by poor management and
OL,14,Fan inappropriate allocation of public
OL,15,Ffunds.
OL,17,FOpen Seas director Phil Taylor said:
OL,18,F"Catching up to deadlines is one
OL,19,Fthing, but consistently failing to
OL,20,Fdeliver on promises for our seas is a
OL,21,Fcrisis.
