OL,3,CScottish Government 'floundering' on
OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,F"We were promised control,
OL,7,Fsustainability and healthy seas but
OL,8,Fwe're seeing ongoing failures and
OL,9,Fcontinued degradation of the marine
OL,10,Fenvironment, with marine protection
OL,11,Fpolicies lagging far behind.
OL,13,F"The Scottish Government needs to
OL,14,Fprioritise the health of our marine
OL,15,Fecosystems, and we urge them to stop
OL,16,Ffloundering and start delivering."
OL,18,FIn total 29 FMPs were scheduled for
OL,19,Fpublication in 2024 across the four UK
OL,20,Fnational governments.
