OL,4,Cfisheries plans, marine charity says
OL,6,FOpen Seas acknowledged that other
OL,7,Fnational governments were also
OL,8,Fconsulting on delays to their FMPs,
OL,9,Fbut said the "majority" of the delays
OL,10,Fwere coming from Scotland.
OL,12,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,13,Fpointed out that the consultation
OL,14,Fwould see two fisheries merged into
OL,15,Fone, thereby reducing the number of
OL,16,FFMPs directly led by Scottish
OL,17,FGovernment to 21.
